          <div class="card-body">
            <h1 class="text-center">About VIT HOSTELS</h1>
            <h3>What is this for?</h3>
            <hr>
            <p>
              <strong class="text-danger">VIT HOSTELS</strong> is a hostels reviewing website. Users can add their hostels or review others' hostels. To get started, simply
              <a href="/register">sign up</a>.
            </p>
            <p>
              This was a project for a IWP course taught by Naveen Sir. It was created using Node.js, Express, and MongoDB.
            </p>
            <h3>Features</h3>
            <hr>
            <ul>
              <li>Users can add, edit, and remove hostels</li>
              <li>Users can review hostels once, and edit or remove their review</li>
              <li>User profiles have more information on the user, such as their full name, phone number, join date, added hostels, and the option to edit their profile or delete their account</li>
              <li>Search Hostels by name</li>
              <li>Sort Hostels by highest rating, most reviewed, lowest price, or highest price</li>
            </ul>
